<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Konrad von Aufseß, Hofmeister Bischof Friedrichs III. von Bamberg</head><p>Der Rat bittet für Hans und H. Paudler von Buckenhofen, Armmänner von St. Sebald zu Nürnberg, um Einhaltung der mit Peter Volckamer und Stefan Koler, Ratsherrn und Bürger zu Nürnberg, vereinbarten Fristverlängerung der bischöflichen Steuerforderungen</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_402" id="200r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_402_r2l4"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> von Aufſeſʒ Rıtter hofmeiſter etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_402_r2l5"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her hofmeiſter . Als
                        vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_402_r2l6"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . von der <expan>anſtellu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
                        wegen . Als <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> lieb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_402_r2l7"><expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd Ratgeſellen
                                <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>volk<ex>mer</ex></expan> vnd <expan>St<ex>efan</ex></expan> Coler mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_402_r2l8"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> gnedigen </del>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> beredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_402_r2l10">Alſo <add><ab facs="#facs_402_line_1577281944409_5579">hat vns
                                        <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> auch </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> iſt <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> aber für
                            vns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan></del>
<expan>han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Ryeter </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_402_r2l11">pfleger des <expan>gotſh<ex>aus</ex></expan> hie cʒu
                        ſant Sebolt / <del rend="strikethrough">vnd </del> auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_402_r2l12">
<expan>fürbr<ex>aht</ex></expan> vvie <del rend="strikethrough">ſolch
                                    <expan>anſtellu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> an dem </del> hanſen vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_402_r2l15"><expan cert="unknown">h</expan>  . <del rend="strikethrough"> den </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_402_r2l13">die </ab></add> pawdler <del rend="strikethrough">n </del>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>pucke<ex>n</ex>hofe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_402_line_1577281956435_5592"><expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>gotſh<ex>aus</ex></expan> Armlewte </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> gemant ſein
                        <expan>vvorde<ex>n</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_402_r2l16">
<add><ab facs="#facs_402_r1l1"><expan>gelobe<ex>n</ex></expan> muſten
                            </ab></add> ſich <expan>cʒeſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan> nü auf den Suntag
                        Jnuocauit / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_402_r2l17">Jr <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Arme<ex>n</ex>lewte<ex>n</ex></expan> darynn ewr günſtıge
                                <expan>furdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_402_r2l19">beweiſen wöllet damit ſıe bey <del rend="strikethrough">ſölch </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_402_r2l18">der <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
</ab></add>
<expan>anſtallu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>bleıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_402_r2l20">
<del rend="strikethrough">als <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> dy
                                    <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Ratgeſelle<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_402_r2l21">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> beredt
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> Als etc das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_402_r2l23"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vȷ̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>icam</expan> Jnuocauit </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_402" id="200r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> von Aufsesz, ritter, hofmeister etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her hofmeister, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehst
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von der <expan>anstellu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
                        wegen, als <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> lieb <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
                        und ratgesellen <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Volk<ex>mer</ex></expan> und <expan>St<ex>efan</ex></expan> Coler mit
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> beredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, also
                            <add>hat uns <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> auch</add>
<expan>Han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Ryeter, pfleger des
                            <expan>gotsh<ex>aus</ex></expan> hie czu sant Sebolt, auch
                                <expan>fürbr<ex>aht</ex></expan>, wie Hansen und <expan cert="unknown">H.</expan>
<add>die</add> Pawdler <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Pucke<ex>n</ex>hofe<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <add><expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>gotsh<ex>aus</ex></expan> armlewte</add>,
                                    <add><expan>gelobe<ex>n</ex></expan> musten</add>, sich
                            <expan>cze stelle<ex>n</ex></expan> nü auf den <app>
<note><q type="date">suntag invocavit</q>01.03.1422</note>
</app>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                            <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex>lewte<ex>n</ex></expan> darynn ewr günstige
                                <expan>furdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> beweisen wöllet, damit sie bey
                            <add>der <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan></add>
<expan>anstallu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>bleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>icam</expan> invocavit.</ab>
</div>
